'''Akarere k’Elmadağ''' (izina mu [[giturukiya]] : ''Elmadağ ilçesi'' ) ni akarere kari mu [[Intara y’Ankara|ntara y’Ankara]] y’igihugu cya [[Turukiya]]. Akarere k’Elmadağ ni kamwe mu turere 16 tugize Intara y’Ankara. Akarere gatuwe n’abaturage bagera kuri 42.511 (abagabo 21.516 n’abagore 20.995)<ref>[http://report.tuik.gov.tr/reports/rwservlet?adnksdb2=&report=idari_yapi_2008.RDF&p_il1=6&p_yil=2008&desformat=html&ENVID=adnksdb2Env  TÜİK]</ref> , batuye kubuso bwa km² 568,07 .

== Izina ==
Iryo zina ryakomotse ku magambo 2 yo m’ururimi rw’igiturukiya ariyo («'''elma'''» 'pome' na «'''dağ'''» 'umusozi').

